Sapio club sibling members are siblings with annual membership subscription with the club and are entitled to several benefits of the club amongst which are entertainment, events, shopping, health, business, hotels and a lots more.

Membership

Membership is "only by invitation" and upon payment of vetting fees, there will be series of verification process by the board within a stipulated time which will determine whether or not the invited personnel is eligible for membership. There are a number of membership category and different annual membership fee applies once confirmed eligible for membership by the board.

  1. Non Resident - $200 per month (limited benefits)
  2. Life membership - $50,000 annually
  3. Individual Membership - $2000 annually
  4. Spouse Membership - $3800 annually
  5. Diplomatic Membership(for selected and notable personnels) - $5000 annually
  6. Corporate Membership
